{
  "texts": [
    "At times, companies need to add custom rules tailored to their needs, so as to enhance the capabilities of the SIEM solution they are using.",
    "However, not all solutions allow customization.",
    "In this feature, we examine the rule customization capability of the targeted SIEM system.",
    "The integrity of logs is very important for any SIEM system.",
    "If an adversary deletes legitimate events from the log while it is in transit from the agent to the SIEM server, correlation rules will not be fired and alarms will not be generated."
  ]
}